  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the crumbled bread, kimchi, and cold water, mixing well.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the olive oil, smoked paprika, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the wet ingredients to the dry ingredients and mix until a crumbly mixture forms.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the casserole from the oven and let it cool for 10 minutes before serving.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional kimchi if desired."
